title: Blood Anthem Mauling Memoirs VI Runescape PK Video
description:
This is the first video from Fear Figments pure Blood Anthem. This video was released in late &#039;07. Blood Anthem is a very unique pure, who is under 70 combat with 99 magic. He uses granite and obby mauls almost exclusively in addition to barrage and blitz spells, and the combos that are pulled off on the low defense targets are unreal even in light of pure videos.

This film was edited in windows movie maker, and is very high quality despite the lack of editing resources.

Enjoy
